&lt;P&gt;Also, XP in the zone hasn't changed one whit.&amp;nbsp; It's the same as its ever been.&amp;nbsp; Of course, as you level up, the XP they give is going to be less because the NPCs levels aren't going up while yours are...same as everywhere else.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
