&lt;P&gt;As to the xp, the con change did indeed change the xp in this zone. You can compare the current xp off light blue/green at 75 to any equivalent non-raid mobs in other zones and find them equal. In the past, any time raid level mobs became groupable/soloable due to increase in level etc, the xp those fewer people then got was significantly more than any equivalent non-raid flagged mob, which should be the case here yet isn't. I hope this now conveys my point better.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
